comment1.params=n
comment1.target=long\ fib(int)
comment1.text=\r\n\ \r\n\ R(5)\ \=\ 15\r\n\ \r\n\ R(100)\ \=>\ 2.7\ *\ 10^17\r\n\ \r\n\ R(n)\ \=>\ (3/2)^(n-1)\r\n\ \r\n\ R(k)\ \=>\ (3/2)^(k-1)\ \ ipotesi\ induttiva\r\n\ \r\n\ per\ n>1\:\ \r\n\ R(n)\ \=\ 1\ +\ R(n-2)\ +\ R(n-1)\r\n\ \r\n\ R(0)\ \=\ 1\ \=>\ (3/2)^(0-1)\ \=\ 2/3\r\n\ R(1)\ \=\ 1\ \=>\ (3/2)^(1-1)\ \=\ 1\r\n\ \r\n\ per\ n>1\:\ \r\n\ R(n)\ \=\ 1\ +\ R(n-2)\ +\ R(n-1)\r\n\ \ \ \ \ \ \=>\ 0\ +\ (3/2)^(n-3)\ +\ (3/2)^(n-2)\r\n\ \ \ \ \ \ \=\ (3/2)^(n-3)\ +\ (3/2)^(n-2)\ *\ ((3/2)^(-1)\ +\ 1)\r\n\ \ \ \ \ \ \=\ (3/2)^(n-2)\ *\ ((3/2)^(-1)\ +\ 1)\ \r\n\ \ \ \ \ \ \=\ (3/2)^(n-2)\ *\ (2/3\ +\ 1)\ \r\n\ \ \ \ \ \ \=\ (5/3)\ *\ (3/2)^(n-2)\ \r\n\ \ \ \ \ \ >\ (3/2)^(n-1)\r\n\ \ \ \ \ \ \r\n\ \ \ \ \ \ 5/3\ >\ 3/2\ <\=\=>\ 10>9\ \ VERO\r\n\ \ \ \ \ \ \r\n\ \ \ \ \ \ \r\n\ \ \ \ \ \ DynamicProgramming.fibMem(100)\ -->\ -1869596475\ \ (int)\r\n\ \ \ \ \ \ Va\ in\ OVERFLOW...\ \r\n\ \ \ \ \ \ L'unica\ opzione\ a\ disposizione\ nei\ tipi\ semplici\ \u00E8\ cambiare\ a\ long\ 10^18\ (x2\ dei\ byte)\r\n\ \ \ \ \ \ \r\n\ \ \ \ \ \ DynamicProgramming.fibMem(100)\ -->\ 1298777728820984005\ \ \ (long)\r\n
